<p>Miss Thevenet is a keen skier who speaks four languages, helped by growing up in Chile, Indonesia and Belgium.</p>

<p>She moved to Britain six years ago and has a masters degree in investment and finance from Queen Mary University of London.</p>

<p>James latest post comes after he revealed that he also treated his French financier partner, who he proposed to in October 2019, to a philanthropic gift - having bought her a piece from a jewellery collection which benefits the Save the Children’s COVID-19 Emergency Response.</p>

